Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Kamala has been there for almost 4 years, and she didn’t CREATE wealth. She DESTROYED 22% of the value of every dollar in your pocket— She didn’t SUPPORT domestic manufacturing. She KILLED 24,000 U.S. manufacturing jobs last month alone."
